@103369 = ~Ring of Onslaught~
@103370 = ~The Ring of Onslaught is the opposite to the Ring of Mentality. It improves the characteristics that are important to those who prefer the power to magic. At the same time, the ring decreases other characteristics.

STATISTICS:

Equipped abilities:
