@104136 = ~Daelan Red Tiger is a noble warrior from the Uthgardt tribes of the north. His father was an orc and his mother was an Uthgardt of the Red Tiger tribe. He never knew his father - his mother never spoke of him. However, Daelan heard rumors that his father was a vile beast who forced himself on his mother during a raid. Daelan was raised by his mother among the Red Tiger tribe in the customs and traditions of the Uthgardt people. Uthgardts are tribal hunters and warriors who live off the land. The orcs are his tribe's most hated enemies, so they accepted him but he was a living reminder of their worst foe. After the death of his mother, his tribe cast him out, but it is not as if they abandoned him in the cold. They gave him food and weapons before they sent him out into the world to prove himself. Once he can show the spirit of the Uthgardt is pure within him the Red Tiger tribe will welcome him back.~
